Siau3-lian5-lang5 chhoe7-tioh8 chit8 e5 thau5-lou7. Thau5-ke ka7 iok-sok: “Goeh8-kip ban7-gou7 (1 ban7 5 chheng), koh lai5 chit8 ko3 goeh8 ke chit8 chheng khou.”
Siau3-lian5--e5 thiaN-liau2, ka7 thau5-ke kong2: “Na7 an2-ne, goa2 koh chit8 ni5 chiah lai5 siong7-pan, kau3-si5 goa2 e5 goeh8-kip si7 2 ban7 7 chheng khou.”
</CL>
